      • ShardObject

        public ShardObject​(java.lang.String name,
                   java.lang.String description,
                   Owner location)
        The main constructor for ShardObjects. If the description is omitted, it is replaced by the given name. If the location is omitted, an empty Room is used.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the object (try to make it unique).
        description - Description of the object (objects with the same name should have the same description but it's not required).
        location - Location of the object.
